 ‘know their numbers’ and contribute to their treatment (self weighing, opening packs, self needling, machine</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> operation). There is evidence of</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> better treatment compliance under this scheme.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">There is also a concern that </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">disparate members of the care team can all provide the same level of care.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">There is some evidence that protocols can improve this.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Personalised services will require greater time input and planning.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">May 2013</span></p></div></body></html>